description:
Special Guests:  GLENN GREENWALD, Pulitzer Prize winning journalist.   NICK CRUSE, co-founder of the Fred Hampton Leftist Network.

Featuring Stef Zamorano and Mike MacRae.   Phone calls from Vince Vaughn, Joe Biden, Noam Chomsky, and Barack Obama.
